		chattext3 = '我的梦想就是让艾纳餐馆成为阿罗拉最好的餐馆！',
		chattext3_tw = '如果用心看，你能看到食材散發出的光。那是廚師的直覺！',
		chattext3_en = 'If you look at it with your heart, you can see the light emitted by the ingredients. That\'s the chef\'s intuition!',
